Project Title: Project Selection Note

Selected Dataset:
BanMANI Dataset

Project Name:
Identifying Manipulated Social Media News in Bangla

Why We Selected This Project:
1. This project focuses on an important and relevant issue: manipulated news on social media.
2. The BanMANI dataset is already prepared for this exact problem, so it is suitable for our course work.
3. The dataset includes real Bangla news examples and helps us work on a meaningful local-language problem.
4. The project has clear academic value because it is based on a published research dataset.